<DOCOLDNO>IA058-000949-B023-386</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/library/categories/natsec/bgu258.html 204.71.237.74 19970109191236 text/html 19462
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 19:12:17 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:30:09 GMT
