http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/library/categories/trade/bgup254.html 204.71.237.74 19970109192541 text/html 9806
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 19:25:38 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:30:14 GMT
